data.meta_description: Joseph Preston Wiltshire  (September 29, 1937 - May 8, 2012)   WINONA - Joseph Preston Wiltshire, age 74, died Tuesday May 8, 2012 at Winona Manor Nursing Home in Winona from heart failure.
